UID:-KD4zg1HRjgh0gNR4XAqI
SUMMARY:Spy Masters Academy
DTSTAMP:20260406T013223Z
DTSTART:20260406T163000Z
DESCRIPTION:Class Experience Calling all young secret agents! This time kid
	s are welcome to join action-packed Outdoor Spy Camp\, where kids will tra
	in to become top-notch spies through thrilling challenges\, daring mission
	s\, and teamwork! Obstacle Courses & Ninja Training – Agents-in-training w
	ill test their agility\, speed\, and stealth as they navigate exciting nin
	ja courses\, crawl through the forest and learn to use nature objects to c
	omplete the challenge. Scavenger Hunts & Riddle Solving – Spies must sharp
	en their detective skills by decoding secret messages\, solving riddles\, 
	and uncovering hidden clues to complete their top-secret missions. Nerf Ba
	ttles & Tactical Challenges – Gear up for friendly Nerf wars\, where teamw
	ork and strategy are key to outsmarting the opposition. Agents will also p
	ractice their precision and accuracy with target practice and stealth mane
	uvers. Escape Room-Style Puzzles – Secret agents will work together to cra
	ck codes\, unlock treasure chests\, and solve mind-bending puzzles before 
	time runs out! Outdoor Adventure & Camouflage Training – Spies will blend 
	into their surroundings\, practice silent movement\, and use nature to the
	ir advantage while completing their missions. This high-energy camp is per
	fect for kids who love adventure\, problem-solving\, and action-packed fun
	 in the great outdoors! Are you ready to accept the mission? - follow the 
	ticket link to book the camp!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/det
	ails/spy-masters-academy/18306067/2026-04-06T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Sports 
	& Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/spy-masters-academy/18306
	067/2026-04-06T00
LOCATION:Suncatcher Forest School\, 18701 se 60th st\, Issaquah\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-sports
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT6H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:JWDUR4VML4651BmPYHcS-
SUMMARY:March Madness Watch Party at Five Iron Golf - Seattle Capitol Hill
DTSTAMP:20260406T013223Z
DTSTART:20260406T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Five Iron Golf is your College Basketball HQ this March! Gather
	 your crew and book 1–2 simulator bays for up to 12 people \\(6 people per
	 bay\\) for a bracket-busting watch party experience. Enjoy all-day TV cov
	erage of college basketball alongside cutting-edge golf and multisport sim
	ulators\, a locally-inspired menu\, and custom beverage packages.\n\nBook 
	your watch party for March 19 or 20 and you'll automatically be entered to
	 win a 20-person happy hour with drinks and appetizers — a $1\,000 value!\
	n\nGroup packages can include reserved event space\, team-specific décor\,
	 a dedicated staff member\, full-screen and/or picture-in-picture viewing\
	, a customizable menu\, beverage packages\, free club rentals\, multisport
	 simulators\, and table games. Select the "Small Event" option at booking 
	to ensure simulator bays are placed side-by-side. Availability of select f
	eatures varies by location.\n\nPromotions:\n\nHappy Hour – "It's 5i o'Cloc
	k Somewhere" \\(Monday–Friday\, 3–6 PM\\)\n\nEnjoy $5 bottomless boneless 
	wings\, $10 bottomless bone-in wings\, $5 select beers/cans/cocktails\, $5
	 dips \\(guacamole\, hot honey ricotta\, hummus\\)\, half-off pizzas\, and
	 $5 featured shots. Dine-in only at participating locations\; simulator re
	ntal may be required.\n\n5i After Dark – "Swing In\, For Less"  \\(Sunday–
	Thursday 9 PM to close | Friday–Saturday 10 PM to close\\)\n\nFeatures $29
	/hr simulator rentals plus the same great food and drink specials as Happy
	 Hour\, with wings priced per dozen rather than bottomless. Dine-in only a
	t participating locations\; simulator rental may be required.\n\nhttps://s
	eatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/march-madness-watch-party-at-five-iro
	n-golf-seattle-capitol-hill/18268907/2026-04-06T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Spor
	ts & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/march-madness-watch-party
	-at-five-iron-golf-seattle-capitol-hill/18268907/2026-04-06T00
LOCATION:Five Iron Golf - Seattle Capitol Hill\, 1525 11th Ave Suite 100\, 
	Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-sports
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT12H
END:VEVENT
